-- Monte Paschi's shares dive after ECB stress test results
-- 
-- Mon Oct 27, 2014 04:15AM EDT
-- None



MILAN, Oct 27 (Reuters) - Shares in Italy's Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> fell as much as 15 percent in early trade on Monday after results from a pan-European health check of lenders showed it had a capital shortfall of 2.1 billion euros.

